Description: Ultra-optimized zero-dynamic-allocation C++17 Vietnamese IME for Fcitx5
 An ultra-optimized, zero-dynamic-allocation C++17 Vietnamese Input Method
 Engine (IME) addon for the Fcitx5 framework on Linux. Designed for power
 users who demand microsecond-level input response latency and zero memory
 fragmentation.
